trans-unit.source: Acts as the top of a two-level named hierarchy of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection" /> collections.
trans-unit.target: Actúa como parte superior de una jerarquía con nombre de dos niveles de las colecciones <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection> class is both a root-level <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collection and a container for a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Configuration.RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection> clase es tanto un nivel de raíz <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> colección y un contenedor para un <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> colección.

trans-unit.source: These collections allow you to create named groups of more <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collections, each containing individual named <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> objects.
trans-unit.target: Estas colecciones permiten crear grupos con nombre o varios <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> colecciones, cada persona que lo contiene <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> objetos.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the profile features added to [!INCLUDE[vstecasplong](~/includes/vstecasplong-md.md)], see [NIB: ASP.NET Profile Properties](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/06a7bf4a-a5a2-462d-9793-c79063a2018d).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información acerca de las características de perfil agregados a [!INCLUDE[vstecasplong](~/includes/vstecasplong-md.md)], consulte [NIB: propiedades de perfil de ASP.NET](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/06a7bf4a-a5a2-462d-9793-c79063a2018d).
